<subSubSection pageId="11" pageNumber="76" type="material">
<paragraph pageId="11" pageNumber="76">Material.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="11" pageNumber="76">Described from a male specimen from Tigre (north of Buenos Aires), 15 specimens from the south of Buenos Aires, and an unspecified number of specimens from the Riachuelo channels, close to the mouth of the Rio de la Plata. All the specimens were reared from caterpillars.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
